---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Terms of Use — [PortalName]"
  description="Terms of use for [PortalName]. Information about acceptable use, disclaimers, and limitations of liability."
>
  <section class="py-8 md:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-6">Terms of Use</h1>
      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] [&_h2]:text-[var(--color-text)] [&_strong]:text-[var(--color-text)]">
        <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> [Date]</p>

        <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing and using [PortalName] ("[domain]"), you agree to these Terms of Use.
          If you do not agree, please do not use this site.
        </p>

        <h2>Information Purpose</h2>
        <p>
          [PortalName] is an informational resource that presents publicly available government data
          in a more accessible format. The information on this site is provided for general informational
          purposes only and should not be relied upon as professional advice.
        </p>
        <!-- For YMYL portals, uncomment the appropriate disclaimer: -->
        <!-- HEALTH: This site does not provide medical advice. Consult a healthcare professional. -->
        <!-- FINANCE: This site does not provide financial advice. Consult a financial professional. -->

        <h2>Accuracy and Completeness</h2>
        <p>
          While we strive to present accurate information, we make no warranties about the completeness,
          reliability, or accuracy of the data. Government source data may contain errors, may be
          outdated, or may not reflect current conditions. Always verify important information with
          official government sources.
        </p>

        <h2>No Professional Advice</h2>
        <p>
          Nothing on this site constitutes professional advice of any kind — whether medical, legal,
          financial, or otherwise. Any decisions you make based on information found here are solely
          your responsibility.
        </p>

        <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          The underlying government data presented on this site is in the public domain. Our original
          design, code, text, and organization of the data are copyrighted by Kiznis.Studio. You may
          not scrape, reproduce, or redistribute our site design or original content without permission.
        </p>

        <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>
          This site may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content
          or privacy practices of those sites.
        </p>

        <h2>Advertising</h2>
        <p>
          This site displays advertisements through Google AdSense to support its operation. Ads are
          served by third parties and are subject to their own terms and privacy policies.
        </p>

        <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the fullest extent permitted by law, [PortalName] and Kiznis.Studio shall not be liable
          for any damages arising from your use of or inability to use this site.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may update these terms at any time. Continued use of the site constitutes acceptance
          of any changes.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about these terms? Email <a href="mailto:hello@[domain]">hello@[domain]</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
